": "I know, right! Now let's power it up!", "actor": 501020, "actorName": "Fu Shun", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Let's see... Right, enter name... I'll go with... F-u-s-h-u-n...", "actor": 501020, "actorName": "Fu Shun", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "You're one of those people that use their real name...?", "actor": 501030, "actorName": "Chang Chun", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Yep! I guess it's more immersive that way, you know?", "actor": 501020, "actorName": "Fu Shun", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Here we go! The hero, Fu Shun, has set off on her journey to save the world!", "actor": 501020, "actorName": "Fu Shun", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}], "Then the World was at Peace...": [{"stopbgm": true, "sequence": ["Fu Shun's Great Adventure&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 0.750em;\">Chapter 4 - Then the World was at Peace...</span><br>"]}, {"bgm": "story-china", "bgName": "bg_story_school", "say": "Get that guy! Attack him!", "actor": 501030, "actorName": "Chang Chun", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "I know! Here, have a taste of THIIIIIS!", "actor": 501020, "actorName": "Fu Shun", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Whoooa!", "actorName": "Fu Shun & Chang Chun", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Woohoo! The world has been saved!", "actor": 501020, "actorName": "Fu Shun", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "The graphics and the controls are as retro as you'd expect... but it's surprisingly fun to play...", "actor": 501030, "actorName": "Chang Chun", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Hey, what's this? A scoreboard?", "actor": 501020, "actorName": "Fu Shun", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Huh? There's another name there besides yours...", "actor": 501030, "actorName": "Chang Chun", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "I think it says... A-n-s-h-a...", "actor": 501020, "actorName": "Fu Shun", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "D-do you think that's...", "actor": 501030, "actorName": "Chang Chun", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "There you are, Fu Shun! You've been going around causing trouble again, haven't you?!", "actor": 501010, "actorName": "An Shan", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Oh crap! An Shan?!", "actor": 501020, "actorName": "Fu Shun", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Not only did you break the padlock to the warehouse, you even made a big mess inside!", "actor": 501010, "actorName": "An Shan", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Yikes, let's get outta-", "actor": 501020, "actorName": "Fu Shun", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "You're not going anywhere! And you, Chang Chun! You coaxed her into doing it, didn't you?!", "actor": 501010, "actorName": "An Shan", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "*Gulp*...", "actor": 501030, "actorName": "Chang Chun", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Stay right where you are! You're going to get a severe...", "actor": 501010, "actorName": "An Shan", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "...Hm? Wait, i-isn't this that old...?!", "actor": 501010, "actorName": "An Shan", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "We found it in the warehouse. It was broken, but Akashi fixed it for me!", "actor": 501020, "actorName": "Fu Shun", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "S-she fixed it...", "actor": 501010, "actorName": "An Shan", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "That other name we saw on the scoreboard... wasn't that...", "actor": 501030, "actorName": "Chang Chun", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "BE QUIET! As I was saying: you're both going to get a severe scolding today!", "actor": 501010, "actorName": "An Shan", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Eeek... An Shan's scarier than the final boss when she gets mad...", "actor": 501020, "actorName": "Fu Shun", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "What was that?!", "actor": 501010, "actorName": "An Shan", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "N-nothing! I didn't say anything!", "actor": 501020, "actorName": "Fu Shun", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, {"say": "Also, I'll be seizing this console!", "actor": 501010, "actorName": "An Shan", "nameColor": "#a9f548"}, 